\section{Building a runner for one host namespace}

Both the standalone command and embedded hosts need the same namespace
and state-root configuration, so we centralise runner creation in one
helper.

<<functions>>=
def build_runner(
    *,
    namespace: str = "tutorial",
    state_root: str | Path | None = None,
    shell_runner: Callable[..., object] = run_interactive_shell,
) -> TutorialRunner:
    """Build a tutorial runner for one CLI host namespace."""

    return TutorialRunner(
        StateStore(state_root, namespace=namespace),
        shell_runner=shell_runner,
    )
@

